# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:11
translate spanish whitneyq1_f3e321a1:

    # wt "Did you get along with your dad?"
    wt "¿Te llevabas bien con tu padre?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:13
translate spanish whitneyq1_b6dc01f0:

    # pc "Yeah, we got along really well... up until the last couple of years."
    pc "Sí, nos llevábamos muy bien... hasta los últimos dos años."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:14
translate spanish whitneyq1_847f8a3e:

    # pc "After my mom died, Dad was all I had and I was all he had."
    pc "Después de que mi madre muriera, papá era todo lo que tenía y yo era todo lo que él tenía."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:16
translate spanish whitneyq1_a026c59b:

    # pc "So we did everything together. We would go on little trips, vacations, see all the things we could."
    pc "Así que hacíamos todo juntos. Nos íbamos de excursión, de vacaciones, veíamos todo lo que podíamos."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:17
translate spanish whitneyq1_ab7a70cd:

    # pc "We'd work on the car together, play Nintendo together, shoot pool, build stuff... everything."
    pc "Arreglábamos el coche juntos, jugábamos a la Nintendo juntos, jugábamos al billar, construíamos cosas... de todo."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:18
translate spanish whitneyq1_d4d550f0:

    # pc "Then, I guess I got older and didn't want to hang out with him as much. I wanted to hang out with my friends..."
    pc "Luego, supongo que me hice mayor y ya no quería pasar tanto tiempo con él. Quería salir con mis amigos..."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:19
translate spanish whitneyq1_ce55de45:

    # pc "... and girls."
    pc "... y con chicas."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:21
translate spanish whitneyq1_30cb65fd:

    # wt "That's natural."
    wt "Es natural."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:23
translate spanish whitneyq1_a6a09b67:

    # pc "Yeah. I think he was a little hurt by it though."
    pc "Sí. Aunque creo que eso le dolió un poco."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:24
translate spanish whitneyq1_e31f1d9f:

    # pc "Then he met Lisa."
    pc "Entonces conoció a Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:25
translate spanish whitneyq1_0d700b81:

    # pc "After that, we didn't really spend much time together anymore."
    pc "Después de eso, ya no pasábamos mucho tiempo juntos."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:26
translate spanish whitneyq1_911bbedc:

    # pc "He wanted to be with her all the time."
    pc "Quería estar con ella todo el tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:27
translate spanish whitneyq1_2ab75d25:

    # pc "I get it now. He'd been lonely for so long. I don't know how he did it."
    pc "Ahora lo entiendo. Llevaba mucho tiempo sintiéndose solo. No sé cómo lo hizo."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:29
translate spanish whitneyq1_4ebfb2c5:

    # pc "But at the time, I felt abandoned. First by Mom. Then by him."
    pc "Pero en aquel momento, me sentí abandonada. Primero por mamá. Luego por él."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:30
translate spanish whitneyq1_be2f5876:

    # pc "And I left before we figured things out. And now he's gone."
    pc "Y me fui antes de que pudiéramos aclarar las cosas. Y ahora se ha ido."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:31
translate spanish whitneyq1_cbbd9e6e:

    # pc "Who knows if I'll ever be able to talk to him again?"
    pc "¿Quién sabe si alguna vez podré volver a hablar con él?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:33
translate spanish whitneyq1_f715e566:

    # wt "You will. I'll make sure of it."
    wt "Lo harás. Me aseguraré de ello."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:34
translate spanish whitneyq1_c9a6c3ed:

    # pc "You really think so?"
    pc "¿De verdad lo crees?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:36
translate spanish whitneyq1_a5f155c2:

    # wt "Of course. I wouldn't waste my time trying to do something if I didn't think it would work."
    wt "Por supuesto. No perdería el tiempo intentando hacer algo si no creyera que funcionaría."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:38
translate spanish whitneyq1_973d74dc:

    # wt "It will work. You'll see your dad again. "
    wt "Funcionará. Volverás a ver a tu padre. "

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyConversations/whitneyq1.rpy:39
translate spanish whitneyq1_41a4adbc:

    # pc "I hope so. Thanks Whitney."
    pc "Eso espero. Gracias, Whitney."

